		<dd>&#8212;  Reviewed on Sep. 1, 2010 by GLENDACHEF. </dd><br>
  <dt><span style="color:teal">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span></dt>
		<dd>Delicious!! I recommend microwaving the apples for 3 minutes before baking,
		to soften them. Great dessert - I'll be making it again for the holidays.</dd>
		<dd>&#8212;  Reviewed on August 28, 2010 by BBABS.</dd><br>
</dl>

